.TH btctax-income-clear 1  btctax "btctax manual"
.SH NAME
clear \- Remove the stored full\-return inputs for a tax year (fall back to a raw `tax\-profile`)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBclear\fR <\fB\-\-year\fR> [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Remove the stored full\-return inputs for a tax year (fall back to a raw `tax\-profile`)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-year\fR \fI<YEAR>\fR
The tax year (e.g. 2024)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
